name: AUDIO_MIXING_FINISHED
description:
Occurs when the playback of the local music file finishes.Deprecated:
  This method is deprecated as of v2.4.0. Use AUDIO_MIXING_STATE_CHANGED instead.
       
   
   After you call startAudioMixing to play a local music file, this callback occurs when the playback finishes. If the call of startAudioMixing fails, the ERROR callback returns the error code WARN_AUDIO_MIXING_OPEN_ERROR.
